# Privacy Policy

**Bless Up Daily – Christian Edition** respects your privacy.

We do **not** collect, store, or share any personal information.  
We do **not** track your activity, location, or identity.

All data—such as your share count and badge progress—is stored **locally on your device** using Chrome's secure local storage.  
No data is transmitted to our servers or any third party.

This extension is created to **inspire, uplift, and protect your peace**—without compromising your privacy.

If you choose to subscribe, your payment is handled securely via **Stripe**.  
We do **not** access or retain any payment details.

> Simple. Private. Devotional.
